channel.title: Help please, moreinfo file problems
channel.description:
I'm having trouble with my cheezscape sever. I used this tutorial to get me through: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,5434.msg162208.html#msg162208
I got on fine the first time i tried, Nothing was edited. But when i started editing some stuff, I didn't delete ONE thing, only edited the text where you log on, and it says welcome to sever blah blah blah. I have a perfect compile, and then i close that and hit runserver, and that works fine. But when i try to log in on my name, it says error, and i get the text you see below in the picture in my runserver thing.
What is the moreinfo file anyways? Could somebody help?
Some pics:
[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img371.imageshack.us/img371/7802/errorqj0.png[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img205.imageshack.us/img205/8007/error2nl2.png[/img][/URL]
[URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img291.imageshack.us/img291/7638/hmmjy3.png[/img][/URL]
Thanks
